text: Tanit Phoenix (born 24 September 1980) is a South African super model, actress and makeup artist. She is known for her swimwear and lingerie photo shoots after appearing in a Sports Illustrated Swimsuit Issue in 2003 and in GQ magazine and FHM in the same year. She was born in Durban, KwaZulu-Natal, South Africa. In 2016, she married actor Sharlto Copley.
